{{#> layouts/main title="Invitation to Join Workspace"}}
<p>Hi {{inviteeEmail}},</p>

{{#if inviterName}}
<p>{{inviterName}} has invited you to join <strong>{{workspaceName}}</strong> on {{appName}}.</p>
{{else}}
<p>You've been invited to join <strong>{{workspaceName}}</strong> on {{appName}}.</p>
{{/if}}

<p>You've been assigned the role of <strong>{{assignedRole}}</strong>, which allows you to {{roleDescription}}.</p>

{{> partials/button url=invitationUrl text="Accept Invitation" color="#f6993f"}}

<p>This invitation will expire in 7 days.</p>

<p>If you're having trouble clicking the button, copy and paste the URL below into your web browser:</p>
<p>{{invitationUrl}}</p>

<p class="important">If you weren't expecting this invitation, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
{{/layouts/main}}